Current version: cpc 0.2

  * Fix build with OCaml 3.12
  * Fix build on MacOS X (no blocks support)
  * Fix build on BSD systems (IPPROTO_TCP)
  * Fix cpc_io_wait in detached mode
  * Use #pragma and name attributes for safe functions
  * Use name attributes for cpc_need_cont (internal use)
  * Allow to restart a cancelled timeout
  * Fix cpc_condvar_count

16 November 2010: cpc 0.1

  * Initial public release.
